artikli.opis:
Ni-MH punjiva baterija Mignon 1,2 V FT-1Z
"ready to use" - 1 pcs per bolybag

version: flat top with solder tags

"ready to use"
This new technology combines the advantages
of a primary battery (non-rechargeable battery) with
those of a secondary type battery (rechargeable
battery). The batteries are fully pre-charged and
ready to use at the time of purchase. A particular
feature is the extremely low self discharge and an
optimized shelf life. (similar to alkaline batteries)
After 12 month the battery has a capacity of over 80%.

advantages:
- low self discharge
- pre-charged, ready to use at the time of purchase,
no need to charge before using.
- rechargeable NiMH technology (1000 cycles)
- environment friendly

artikli.opis:
Inteligentna letna baterija DJI Mini 2 odlikuje se velikom energetskom gustoćom 
koja ne samo da smanjuje ukupnu težinu već produžuje maksimalno vrijeme leta na 31 minutu za još više zabave. 
Uz ugrađeni DJI Inteligentni sustav upravljanja baterijama, status baterije se prati i izvještava u stvarnom vremenu, 
što vam omogućuje manje fokusiranja na razinu baterije, a više na letenje. 
Stabilan izlaz energije i precizan izračun preostalog vremena leta dodaju još jedan nivo sigurnosti tijekom leta.

artikli.naziv: Baterija za StromPi3 hat za Raspberry Pi, 1000mAh,Joy-it StromPi3BAT
artikli.opis:
Battery Unit for StromPI 3  
This battery unit forms with the StromPi V3 a wholesome USV solution.  
It is available as a third voltage source and can be monitored and can be automatically recharged.  
It is based of the LiFePo4 technoloy and offers more essential advantages compared to the standard lithium-ION structures:      
increased security because there can not be a chemical spontaneous combustion     
a longer life time as lithium ION technology     more charge cycles     the battery gets automatically charged if it runs with a external voltage source  
In the battery electronic, protection circuits against overload, short-circuits and deep discharging are integrated. 

Specifications

Model
Battery Unit for StromPi 3

Type
Lithium Iron Phosphate (LiFePO4)

Capacity
1000 mAh

Voltage
3,2 V

Special Features
Can be plugged directly onto the StromPi 3, Fully accessible pin header, 
Charges immediately on StromPi 3, Own protection electronics, 
Own charging electronics, Increased safety as chemical self-ignition is not possible, 
Significantly longer life than Lithium ION technologies, 
Wide temperature range

Dimensions
65 x 56 x 20 mm

Weight
52 g

https://joy-it.net/en/products/RB-StromPI3BAT

artikli.naziv: Baterija za StromPi3 hat za Raspberry Pi, 2000mAh,Joy-it StromPi3BAT-XL
artikli.opis:
Extra large Battery Pack  
This battery hat with LiFePO4 battery turns the StromPi V3 into a full-featured UPS solution. 
The replacement battery is provided as third current source, is surveilled and will be recharged automatically. 
With the doubling of the rated capacity, the lifespan is nearly twice as long as well in comparison to the 1000 mAh battery.  
It is based of the LiFePo4 technoloy and offers more essential advantages compared to the standard lithium-ION structures:

artikli.naziv: Baterijska svjetiljka LEDLENSER® P2 BM , blister            (K)
artikli.opis:
Svjetiljka P2 dokazuje da svjetlosni učinak ne ovisi samo o veličini i težini. 
Ova kompaktna svjetiljka, koja spade u kategoriju svjetiljki privjesaka ima jačinu svjetlosti od 16 lumena, duga je 102 mm, a teška samo 36 gr. 
Drugim riječima, lakša je od poklopca baterije velike ručne svjetiljke. 
Baterija joj traje do 7 sati, a ima i leću koja odvaja bijelo od plavog svjetla. 
Samo pritisnite prekidač i vidjet ćete zraku svjetlosti s plavom aureolom u fokusiranom načinu rada. 
Kod svjetiljke P2 nismo štedjeli na ničemu – osim na težini.

Pakiranje dodatno sadrži: 1 set baterija, vezicu za nošenje, privjesak za ključeve, kopču za remen i torbicu


Specifikacije

    Boja: Crna
    Serija: P - Serija
    Vrsta uporabe: Svakodnevna
    Mogućnost punjenja: Ne
    Head diametar: 14,5 mm 

Tehnički detalji
LED 	Led konfiguracija 	1 x Low Power LED
Baterija 	Punjiva        	Ne
	Vrsta baterije 	1 x Micro (AAA) 1.5V
	Kapacitet baterije 	1.88 Wh
Dimenzije Duljina 	102mm
	Težina 	36 g
	Promjer glave 	14,5 mm
Karakteristike
Modovi        	Power 	Jaka svjetlost
Vrsta prekidača 	Prednji / Stražnji 	Stražnji

Napredni sustav fokusiranja – AFS

Galileo se zakleo u snagu leće, a Newton se zakleo u snagu reflektora. 
Mi smo jednostavno ujedinili te dvije tehnologije – i to bolje nego bilo tko prije. 
Rezultat je patentirani napredni sustav fokusiranja (AFS – Advanced Focus System), 
koji omogućuje fokusirani svjetlosni snop za osvjetljivanje dalekih objekata i široki svjetlosni snop za osvjetljavanje širokog polja. 
Pritom je široki svjetlosni snop zadržao homogenost i daje lijepu svjetlost bez ikakvih sjena i smetnji. 
Učinkovitošću AFS sustava oduševljeni su čak i stručnjaci.


Garancija 7 godina !

Mi, Ledlenser Hrvatska, poduzimamo mnogobrojne mjere kako bi osigurali da vaša svjetiljka ima dugogodišnju i pouzdanu uslugu servisa. 
Ako vaš proizvod ima nedostatak u materijalu ili izradi, ne brinite. 
Unutar našeg 5-godišnjeg jamstva ili 7-godišnjeg ako je proizvod registriran, rado ćemo ga popraviti ili zamijeniti s proizvodom jednake ili veće vrijednosti. 
Ovo jamstvo ne obuhvaća zlouporabu, prepravke, krađu, gubitak ili nerazumno korištenje vašeg Ledlenser proizvoda. 
Ovo jamstvo pokriva samo prvobitnog vlasnika i ne odnosi se na futrole, dodatke, tisak ili oštećenja na površinskom premazu.

artikli.naziv: Baterijska svjetiljka LEDLENSER® P6R Signature , kutija        (K)
artikli.opis:
Ledlenser P6R Signature ručna svjetiljka

P6R Signature savršen je izbor za svaku avanturu na otvorenom. 
Izuzetno je robusna i otporna, s tvrdo anodiziranom površinom i zaštitom od vode i prašine IP68. 
Brojne značajke ističu koliko je P6R Signature vrhunska, poput prekidača za odabir načina rada, koji nudi četiri moda, 
dodatno crveno svjetlo sa strane, dimanje i fokusiranje, kao i personalizirane funkcije i sekvence osvjetljenja. 
Praktični zidni nosač s našim sustavom magnetskog punjenja olakšava punjenje svjetiljke.

-        Moćna vrhunska svjetiljka s brojnim dokazanim Ledlenser tehnologijama i prirodnom reprodukcijom boja (CRI80)
-        Prekidač za odabir načina rada s direktnim pristupom svjetlosnim funkcijama – koji se u potpunosti može konfigurirati zahvaljujući tehnologiji Smart Light Technology
-        Crveno pomoćno svjetlo na bočnoj strani kućišta
-        Tvrdo anodizirani materijal pruža dodatnu zaštitu od trošenja i korozije
-        Olakšano punjenje baterije sa zidnim nosačem i sustavom magnetskog punjenja

Pakiranje sadrži: 1 set punjivih baterija, vezicu, kabel za magnetno punjenje, kopča za džep, futrola, USB adapter i materijal za zidnu montažu

	Prikladno za 	Ručne svjetiljke

Napredni sustav fokusiranja – AFS

Galileo se zakleo u snagu leće, a Newton se zakleo u snagu reflektora. Mi smo jednostavno ujedinili te dvije tehnologije – i to bolje nego bilo tko prije. 
Rezultat je patentirani napredni sustav fokusiranja (AFS – Advanced Focus System), koji omogućuje fokusirani 
svjetlosni snop za osvjetljivanje dalekih objekata i široki svjetlosni snop za osvjetljavanje širokog polja. 
Pritom je široki svjetlosni snop zadržao homogenost i daje lijepu svjetlost bez ikakvih sjena i smetnji. 
Učinkovitošću AFS sustava oduševljeni su čak i stručnjaci.

Smart light tehnologija

Ova inovacija omogućuje da uz pomoć mikrokontrolera programirate individualnu kombinaciju funkcija s različitim kombinacijama dodira i pritisaka na prekidač. 
Tako ćete uvijek pri ruci imati optimalni svjetlosni mod.

Kontrola temperature

Ledlenser svjetiljke nikada nisu previše vruće bez obzira koliko ih koristite. 
Tako ćete uvijek biti zaštićeni od opeklina, a LED čip će biti zaštićen od pregrijavanja.

Magnetski sustav punjenja

Osnovna ideja ovakvog načina punjenja je što lakše rukovanje. 
Ono što omogućava takav sustav punjenja je magnetsko sučelje između svjetiljke i punjača. 
Svjetiljku možete umetnuti direktno na punjač dok baterija ostaje u kućištu. 
Vaša svjetiljka tako će vam uvijek biti na pri ruci. 
Zahvaljujući inteligentnoj elektronici ovakav sustav punjenja je ekološki prihvatljiv čak i ako svjetiljku ostavite na punjaču duže vrijeme. 
A uz to sve, izgleda spektakularno.

Svjetlo u slučaju nužde

Ova aplikacija pretvara vaš Ledlenser u svjetlo u slučaju nužde. 
Ukoliko nestane struje, a vaša svjetiljka je na punjaču, ona će se automatski upaliti. 
Svjetlo će vam pomoći da se lakše orijenirate i pronađete, na primjer, ormarić s osiguračima.

Garancija 7 godina !

Mi, Ledlenser Hrvatska, poduzimamo mnogobrojne mjere kako bi osigurali da vaša svjetiljka ima dugogodišnju i pouzdanu uslugu servisa. 
Ako vaš proizvod ima nedostatak u materijalu ili izradi, ne brinite. 
Unutar našeg 5-godišnjeg jamstva ili 7-godišnjeg ako je proizvod registriran, rado ćemo ga popraviti ili zamijeniti s proizvodom jednake ili veće vrijednosti. 
Ovo jamstvo ne obuhvaća zlouporabu, prepravke, krađu, gubitak ili nerazumno korištenje vašeg Ledlenser proizvoda. 
Ovo jamstvo pokriva samo prvobitnog vlasnika i ne odnosi se na futrole, dodatke, tisak ili oštećenja na površinskom premazu.

P7R Signature je vrhunska, nova verzija ove kultne svjetiljke. 
Ovo je jedna od naših najkvalitetnijih svjetiljka s osvjetljenjem do čak 2000 lumena. 
Robusnost i izdrživost su osigurane uz zaštitu IP68 i tvrdo anodiziranu završnu obradu.

Još neke od fenomenalnih karakteristika ove vrhunske svjetiljke su patentirani napredni sustav fokusiranja,

-        Tvrdo anodizirani materijal pruža dodatnu zaštitu od trošenja i korozije

artikli.opis:
Ledlenser H5 Core Crna naglavna svjetiljka

Ako se želite sigurno kretati u mraku i istovremeno imati slobodne ruke, treba vam Ledlenser naglavna svjetiljka. 
Naši modeli su izrazito lagani i udobni za nošenje, pružaju svjetlost vrhunske kvalitete, nude mnogobrojne funkcije i mogu se potpuno prilagoditi vašim potrebama.

artikli.opis:
snažna punjiva naglavna svjetiljka      

Isporuka sa dvije punjive litijeve baterije

Snažno, vodootporno prednje svjetlo sa 6 W CREE LED.

Izvor svjetlosti je CREE XM-L T6 dioda visokog intenziteta od 6 W koja nudi jak svjetlosni tok od 570 lm. 
Svjetlo prednjeg svjetla svjetli do 500 m, a opremljeno je funkcijom Zoom koja ručno produžuje objektiv za 
veće udaljenosti i obrnuto kada je leća umetnuta za rasipanje svjetlosti.

Prednje svjetlo nudi tri standardna načina rada: potpuno svjetlo, uštedu energije i treperenje. 
Za prebacivanje između različitih načina rada, koristite gumb za uključivanje / isključivanje na vrhu prednjeg svjetla.

Napajanje se rješava s dvije 3.7V baterije kapaciteta 2800 mAh. Izmjerena izdržljivost je dobrih 8 sati. 
Akumulatori se postavljaju u kućište koje je postavljeno na stražnjoj strani glave sa stražnje strane i 
povezano je sa samom rasvjetom pomoću kabela koji se protežu na jedan od tri remena. 
Kućište akumulatora svijetli crveno kako bi se osigurala sigurnost, primjerice pri kretanju uz rub ceste.

Prednje svjetlo također ima IP44 stupanj zaštite i zbog toga je zaštićeno od prskanja.

Ledenser ručne svjetiljke stvorene su za ljude koji vole uzeti stvar u svoje ruke. 
Bez obzira radi li se o svakodnevnoj upotrebi, hobiju ili poslu, od Ledlenser svjetiljki uvijek možete očekivati maksimalnu svjetlost uz minimalnu potrošnju energije. 
U brojkama to znači ukupnu količinu svjetla do 3200 lumena, domet svjetlosti  do 700 m i trajanje baterije do 40 sati. 
Iznimnu izvedbu ručnih svjetiljki upakirali smo u višestruko nagrađivani dizajn.

P6R Core je ručna svjetiljka koja je potpuno zaštićena od prašine i vode. 
Elegantan dizajn ove svjetiljke spaja modernu tehnologiju s vrhunskim osvjetljenjem. 
P6R Core predstavlja automatsko zatamnjenje  zahvaljujući inovativnoj Smart Light tehnologiji, a može se napuniti sustavom magnetskog punjenja. 
Ima i patentirani sustav naprednog fokusa, čak i pod vodom, u kombinaciji s Multi-Core Optics tehnologijom.

U načinu primanja zvuka možete primati zvuk s bilo kojeg pametnog telefona, prijenosnog računala ili tableta s omogućenim Bluetooth®-om 
na bilo koji audio sustav ili zvučnike. Pomoću ulazno / izlaznog priključka AUX možete jednostavno povezati ovaj uređaj s drugim audio uređajem.

artikli.opis:
The Falcon HD Wireless HDMI Transmitter guarantees loss-free wireless transmission of HDMI signals in FullHD and 3D. Transmission of the entire 1080p information with very low latency of less than 0.5 seconds is ensured over a range of 30 m with a clear line of sight. In addition, IR signals from the remote control are also transmitted reliably. The Qualcomm Atheros chipset provides for the necessary processing power for the wireless transmission is an optimum manner. The PureVu CNW8302 FullHD media processor ensures loss-free video processing in precise detail. It goes without saying that the Falcon HD is HDCP-compliant and energy-efficient. Thanks to its compact dimensions, it offers many varied set-up options and flexibility.

It is not without good reason that the AR9374 wi-fi chip from Qualcomm is the first choice in any devices with high demands concerning data throughput, range and operating stability for wireless data transmission. Its extremely compact format allows the problem-free elimination of any scattering signals, meaning that it can be integrated into our high-quality Oehlback products. With dual-band wi-fi 802.11n, signals up to 300 Mbit/s are transmitted, with the AR9734 providing excellent signal stability even at maximum range.

Stripping tool

for round cables

For precise and safe stripping. 



Product description
When stripping round and moisture proof cables, access is often difficult, as the junction or 
distribution boxes are usually situated in ceilings or inside switch cabinets. 
The stripping tool for round cables makes working in difficult-to-access spots exceptionally easy. 
Thanks to the rounded tool head and the elongated ergonomic handle shape, the stripping tool fits perfectly into your hand, 
offering increased comfort even in work areas that are difficult to access. 
The tool ensures reliable stripping of all standard round cables with diameters from 6 – 13 mm, without the need for setting the cutting depth manually in advance. 
Furthermore, the length arrester integrated into the housing supports particularly precise working when processing series with the same stepped dimensions. 
The fastening clip for storage ensures safe keeping and prevents damage to the tool.
Application
For flush stripping of round and moisture proof cables with diameters 6 – 13 mm (e.g. NYM 3 x 1.5 mm2 to 5 x 2.5 mm2), 
also for hard-to-reach locations e.g. ceiling and wall areas, in junction boxes, distribution boxes, switch cabinets etc.

artikli.opis:
The acoustic quality of premium hifi components has a life cycle that is difficult to bring in line with the volatility of current technology. Thanks to the BTT 5000 proud owners of powerful hifi systems now no longer need to despair when it comes to uncomplicated wireless streaming from various music sources. The compact Bluetooth transmitter forms a flexible link between the classic hifi world and modern music streaming. Thanks to the supplied 3.5mm jack cable, the BTT 5000 can be connected to any device with the corresponding output. aptX guarantees an artefact-free transmission of the signal in CD quality. A special feature of the BTT 5000 is its "dual pairing" mode, which enables two devices to be connected to the transmitter simultaneously.

artikli.opis:
Bežični WLAN zvučnik

CS 40 je veći od dva zvučnika novog Magnat sustava s mogućnošću reprodukcije u više prostorija. WLAN zvučnik je bežično integriran u vašu kućnu mrežu zahvaljujući ugrađenom Wi-Fi modulu te nudi glazbeni užitak uz jednostavan pritisak gumba. Osim reprodukcije vlastite glazbene knjižnice putem tehnologije DLNA, model CS 40 također omogućava pristup internet radiju i podršku za pretplatnički glazbeni servis Spotify. Zvučnikom se upravlja pomoću aplikacije AllPlay Jukebox za Androd i iOS. Osim uobičajenih mogućnosti reprodukcije, aplikacija se također koristi za individualnu kontrolu glasnoće svih zvučnika i kombiniranje pojedinih komponenti u grupu. Nadalje, modernom komponentom sa završnom obradom u crnoj boji s metalnom rešetkom boje antracita, također se može upravljati i direktno uz pomoć tri senzorska gumba.

mikro bušenje, čišćenje i poliranje. Vreteno se vrti između preciznih kugličnih ležajeva, a podiže se tasterom za blokiranje.
20- milimetarski rukavac bušilice odgovara MICROMIT nosaču bušilice.
Bušilica je opremljena specijalnim, izbalansiranim, tihim istosmjernim i dugovječnim motorom. 
Trajno kućište od POLIAMIDA ojačano sa staklenim vlaknima sa mekim komponentama na područjima zahvata prstima.

artikli.naziv: CAN modul sa MCP2515, Joy-IT SBC-CAN01
artikli.opis:
CAN Module

This universally applicable CAN module is based on the known MCP2515 controller. 
It is provided each with a CAN and a SPI interface. 
Moreover, it comes with a terminating resistor of 120 ? which ensures the capacity of 
propulsion and the long-distance data transmission against the radiation of signal.

This module is compatible to all Raspberry and Arduino as well as the most of other microcontrollers.

Specifications

Model            CAN Module
Chipset          MCP2515, TJA1050
CAN Specification         CAN V2.0B
Communicationspeed    1 Mb/s
Oscillator                       8MHz Crystal Oscillator
Termination Resistors:
120 ? with impedance adjustment 
(ensures drive capacity and long-distance data transmission against signal radiation)

Interface                         SPI, CAN
Input Voltage                   5 V
Power Consumption         5 mA
Standby current               1 µA
Operating temperature     -40°C - 85°C
Compatible to:
Arduino, Raspberry Pi and other common microcontrollers
Dimensions                      44 x 34 x 14 mm
Weight                             8 g

CodeBug is a cute, programmable and wearable device designed to introduce simple 
programming and electronic concepts to anyone, at any age.

It is easy to program CodeBug using the online interface, which features colourful drag and drop blocks, 
an in-browser emulator and engaging community features. 
Create your own games, clothes, robots or whatever other wacky inventions you have in mind! 
CodeBug has six electrical legs that can be used with external electronic components 
Such as LEDs and switches. 
You can connect to the legs with croc­clips, banana­plugs or conductive thread. 
The centre two legs provide power and the other four legs are selected as input 
or outputs in your code. 
The state of the inputs can be read, and the outputs turned on or off from statements in your code.

Includes:

    CodeBug
    microB USB cable for programming and power
    Quick start guide 

CodeBug is compatible with Windows, Mac OSX, and Linux. 
No drivers need to be installed (it will appear as a portable disk). 
There are great projects and activities to be found on the CodeBug learning centre.

Features:

    25 LED display (5 x 5 red pixels)
    2 buttons
    Make your projects mobile using a cell battery
    4 touch sensitive I/O pads
    Micro USB socket
    Expansion port for I2C, SPI and UART
    Blockly-based online programming interface
    CodeBug emulator for checking code before downloading
    Online project storage and sharing
    Tethered mode for computer/CodeBug interaction
    Step-by-step walkthrough guides

We bring you the Maker UNO, an Arduino UNO compatible board designed and developed specially for students to learn coding and microcontroller. 
We named it Maker UNO to encourage everyone to be a maker by getting started with this amazing board. 
By the way, it is in PURPLE!

3 years ago, we re-engineered Arduino UNO and introduce CT-UNO. 
It has been used in many projects development, among students, engineers, teachers, and makers. 
We have also been conducting training using CT-UNO for several years, and from the observations 
and feedback gathered; there are some features are under-utilized, yet there are some features which are needed for beginner. 
Working hand in hand with ARUS and rero team, we initiate the redesign of CT-UNO, 
making it more affordable, and more beginner friendly.  
It is Arduino UNO R3 compatible, and by that, Maker UNO can be programmed via Arduino IDE 
and compatible with all the example code and libraries for Arduino UNO. 

Maker-UNO has all the amazing features Arduino UNO has to offer, 14 Digital I/O pins with 6 PWM pins, 6 Analog inputs, UART, SPI, external interrupts, not to forget the I2C too. The SDA, SCL and IOREF pins which being broken out on UNO R3 are on MAKER-UNO too. We has also populated the ISP header pins (SPI and power). With this, Maker-UNO will be compatible with all Arduino UNO shield.

Features:
SMD ATmega328P microcontroller(the same microcontroller on Arduino UNO) with Optiboot (UNO) Bootloader.
USB Programming facilitated by the CH340.
Input voltage: USB 5V, from computer, power bank or standard USB adapter.
500mA (maximum) 3.3V voltage regulator.
0-5V outputs with 3.3V compatible inputs.
14 Digital I/O Pins (6 PWM outputs).
6 Analog Inputs.
ISP 6-pin Header.
32k Flash Memory.
16MHz Clock Speed.
R3 Shield Compatible.
LED array for 5V, 3.3V, TX, RX and all digital pins.
On board programmable push button (pin 2, need to configure as INPUT_PULLUP).
On board piezo buzzer (pin 8).
Utilize USB Micro-B socket.

Maker UNO User's Manual:
https://docs.google.com/document/d/1gJIF-tssdoxk8qAq2aHBmPwVHulFL_lSElOhA17Du64/edit#

artikli.naziv: Cytron UNO Special Edition - Arduino Compatible
artikli.opis:
We have CT-UNO, our version of Arduino UNO. 
Now this is special edition of CT-UNO and we called it Cytron UNO Special Edition.

What is so special about Special Edition :) The SE comes with special side connectors. 
With these connectors, CT-UNO is able to be stack on TOP or Bottom of shield.

Anyway, here is CT-UNO vs Arduino UNO.

Basically CT-UNO-SE is Arduino UNO R3 with special side connectors. 
CT-UNO-SE is exactly the same as CT-UNO, except for the side connectors :)

The CT-UNO combines the simplicity of the UNO Optiboot bootloader (which load program faster), 
The stability of the FTDI and the R3 shield compatibility of the latest Arduino UNO R3.

Features:

    SMD ATmega328 microcontroller with Optiboot (UNO) Bootloader.
    USB Programming Facilitated by the Ubiquitous FTDI FT231X (more stable).
    Input voltage: DC7-15V.
    1A (maximum) 5V voltage regulator.
    500mA (maximum) 3.3V voltage regulator.
    0-5V outputs with 3.3V compatible inputs.
    14 Digital I/O Pins (6 PWM outputs).
    6 Analog Inputs.
    ISP 6-pin Header.
    32KByte Flash Memory.
    SRAM: 2KByte
    EEPROM: 1KByte
    16MHz Clock Speed.
    R3 Shield Compatible.
    TX, RX, Power, pin 13 LEDs are moved to edge.
    Utilize USB Micro-B socket.
    White PCB!
    Special version of site connector (CT-UNO-SE only)

artikli.naziv: Daljinski upravljač za STRONG TV SRT32HX/ HY4003

artikli.opis:
Description :

POWER HAS TO BE CONECTED TO THE MODULE !!

    As everyone at some point will recognize the Raspberry Pi doesn't include any kind of shutdown button. 
    So the only way to power it off is by unplugging it from the power supply.
    To make sure you get no corruption of your data files on the SD card you should shutdown 
     the Raspberry before powering it off.
    So the whole procedure can be a bit annoying especially if you want to use the Raspberry as 
    some kind of embedded PC . e.g. a media server or an internet radio.
    
Features: 
    Power Button provides a small circuit that includes the features:
    Sending a shutdown signal to the Raspberry if the Shutdown Button is pressed
    Powering off the Raspberry after save shutdown
    Powering on the Raspberry after the Button is pressed again
    LED light indicating the current state: On / Shutdown / Off
    Easy to set
    Easy to setup
    Dimension: 65mm x 30 mm x 20mm

Parameters:
Function	       BCM	           RPi
Disk Status	21          	Pin 40
Shut Down	24    	Pin 18
PWR Status	26	        Pin 37
GND        	N/A   	Pin 6/9/14/20/25/30/34/39
5V            	5V     	Pin 2/4

artikli.opis:
Professional wall detector can be used to detect metal, wood and AC cable hidden in the wall. 
It is suitable for house decoration or refurbishment.

Features:
Professional wall detector can be used to detect metal, wood and AC cable hidden in the wall.
Keep the instrument close to the wall and slowly move it. When it has detected metal, wood or AC cable, it will display the signal strength and beep.
According to signal strength, you can judge the exact location of the materials which can avoid drilling failure.
The detector can detect an AC cable with a voltage higher than 110V, 50-60Hz, the sensibility may be weak when the cable is grounded.
The ZOOM key is helpful to detect small things or things buried in deep.
High accuracy, with a maximum detection depth of 80mm.
Portable size, convenient to use.

Note:
Clean the detector with dry and soft cloth. Do not clean it with detergents or other chemicals.

DVT2000 diktafon je idealan za snimanje razgovora u stereo MP3 formatu. Uređaj je opremljen sa 2 osjetljiva mikrofona koji omogućavaju snimanje zapisa u visokoj kvaliteti. Zahvaljujući MP3 formatu zapise je lako dijeliti i reproducirati na raznim uređajima.

Veliki display sa osvjetljenjem omogućava laki pregled zapisa. Uređaj ima 4 GB ugrađene memorije te trajanje baterije do 42 sata što omogućava snimanje dugih zapisa.

Uređaj je kompatibilan sa Windows i Mac operacijskim sustavom što omogućava laku reprodukciju, pohranu i dijeljenje zapisa.

Ukoliko vam ugrađena memorija od 4 GB nije dovoljna, ovaj uređaj podržava SD memorijske kartice do 32 GB.

VoiceTracer 2050 je savršen zvučni snimač za snimanje razgovora u pokretu. Zahvaljujući MP3 stereo snimanju uvijek dobivate odličnu kvalitetu zvuka koju sa lakoćom možete podijeliti sa drugima. Dovoljno je samo povezati snimač u vaše računalo na Windows ili Mac OS platformi. Veliki grafički zaslon vam omogućuje da vidite sve važne informacije u trenu, čak i u uvjetima slabije osvijetljenosti, zahvaljujući pozadinskom osvjetljenju zaslona. Sa 8GB interne memorije, vaš snimač je u stanju snimati neprekidno i do nekoliko dana. Gotovo neograničen kapacitet snimanja zahvaljujući Mikro SD memorijskom utoru koji podržava do 32GB dodatne memorije. Visoko-kapacitetna Li-polymerna baterija se može sa lakoćom napuniti putem standardnog mikro USB utora. To garantira produženi životni vijek baterije za duže snimanje i do 50 sati, osiguravajući pritom da vaš snimač uvijek bude spreman za rad kada ste spremni i vi. Uživajte u vašim FM radio stanicama kada i koliko često to poželite. Jednostavno aktivirajte funkciju za snimanje kada čujete vašu omiljenu radio stanicu i dopustite VoiceTraceru da snimi radio signal u MP3 formatu. Pakiranje uključuje snimač zvuka, USB kabel, kratke upute i slušalice.

DVT6010 diktafon metalnog dizajna je idealan za snimanje predavanja, nudi mogućnost zumiranja zvuka sa 3 mikrofona (udaljenost do 15 metara), automatsko podešavanje osjetljivosti i funkcija snimanja zadnjih 5 sekundi prije uključivanja snimanja kako ne biste propustili niti jednu riječ.

DVT6010 diktafon ima ugrađen senzor pokreta te ovisno o položaju (na stolu ili u ruci) odabire mikrofon koji najbolje odgovara situaciji. DVT6010 nudi mogućnost snimanja zadnjih 5 sekundi prije uključivanja snimanja. Uređaj se nalazi u stanju pripravnosti i snima zvuk svakih 5 sekundi bez spremanja. Ova mogućnost nudi spontano snimanje važnih dijelova razgovora.

Zapisi se snimaju u MP3 formatu i zahvaljujući tome lako ih je dijeliti i reproducirati na raznim uređajima. Veliki zaslon u boji nudi oštru sliku i samim time olakšava vidjeti sadržaj i zapise koji se nalaze na njemu. Korisničko sučelje podržava 8 jezika i optimiziran je za lagano korištenje. Svi zapisi se pohranjuju sa datumom i vremenom snimanja kako biste ih lakše mogli pronaći u datoteci.

Uređaj ima ugrađenu punjivu bateriju koja puni putem USB kabela, a osigurava trajanje snimanja do 50 sati. Ukoliko vam ugrađena memorija od 8 GB nije dovoljna, ovaj uređaj podržava SD memorijske kartice do 32 GB.

artikli.naziv: DJ gramofon PIONEER PLX-500 K Black
artikli.opis:
Vinyl revolution: Introducing the PLX-500 – Direct drive turntable for DJs and vinyl lovers

We’re releasing a new direct drive turntable to offer a more versatile vinyl solution for DJing and leisurely listening at a competitive price. The PLX-500 is ready to use straight out of the box thanks to its line output, which lets you plug it into your sound system or powered speakers with no need for an external amplifier.

Drawing on our heritage in making high-quality decks, the PLX-500 inherits the layout of the PLX-1000 professional turntable and produces warm, clear analogue sound. The high-torque deck is ideal for scratching and comes with everything you need including a cartridge, stylus and slipmat, and its USB out means you can easily make high-quality digital recordings of your vinyl collection in our free rekordbox software. You can use the PLX-500 and the rekordbox dvs Plus Pack to play and scratch digital files when you combine them with a compatible DJM mixer and the RB-VS1-K Control Vinyl. And you can choose between the black (PLX-500-K) and white (PLX-500-W) versions to match your set-up or the design of your home.

The PLX-500-K and PLX-500-W are available from September.
PLX-500 KEY FEATURES

    High-quality analogue vinyl sound
    The PLX-500 series inherits design features from the PLX-1000 professional turntable to produce the high-quality sound you expect from vinyl. The shortest possible audio routing from the stylus to the outputs reduces distortion, and the phono and line outputs mean you can connect directly to your sound system or powered speakers to enjoy warm sound.
    Easy digital recording
    An in-built USB output means you can record your vinyl collection to high-quality digital WAV files by simply connecting the PLX-500 to your PC or Mac. Digitising your tracks is easy using our free rekordbox application and, once they’re in your rekordbox collection, you can play them using the PLX-500 and a rekordbox dvs set-up, or on a DDJ controller, or on CDJs via USB. You can also enjoy them on your mobile devices whenever you want.
    Using its audio analysis technology, rekordbox detects the silence between tracks and creates a separate file in your collection for each one, so you can just press play and record a whole album from an analogue source to individual tracks without resetting the recording in between songs. After you’ve finished recording you can name and tag all your new tracks.
    How to record your vinyl to high-quality digital files:
        Connect the PLX-500 to your computer with a USB cable.
        Open our free rekordbox application (version 4.2.1).
        Click the record button in the software and it enters Record Standby mode.
        Press play on the PLX-500. rekordbox begins recording when the music starts.
        When you’ve finished recording, press stop. A window opens in rekordbox where you can enter information for each track including name and artist. The tracks then appear in your rekordbox collection and you can search for them by name, artist etc.
    High-torque direct drive turntable for DJ performances and rekordbox dvs
    The high-torque, direct drive PLX-500 is ideal for mixing and scratching on. You can also combine it with the rekordbox dvs Plus Pack to play and perform with your digital files when using a compatible DJM mixer and the RB-VS1-K Control Vinyl (available separately).
    Dust cover with record sleeve stand
    You can enjoy the vinyl sound of your records and their artwork at the same time thanks to the dust cover that incorporates a stand for displaying record sleeves when open.
    Layout inherited from the PLX-1000 professional turntable
    The PLX-500 inherits its slick design from the professional PLX-1000 turntable and you can choose between the black (PLX-500-K) and white (PLX-500-W) versions to match the colour of your gear or the interior of your home.

How to use rekordbox dvs:

Buy the RB-VS1-K Control Vinyl from a Pioneer DJ authorised dealer or directly from our website (limited countries only). Visit rekordbox.com to download the latest version of rekordbox for free, then buy rekordbox dj and rekordbox dvs licence keys. Alternatively you can subscribe to rekordbox dj and get rekordbox dvs as part of your subscription plan. Find out more about rekordbox dvs

The silver coloured PC-HS01-S headshell included with the PLX-500 will be available to buy separately from December 2016 in three colour options. Choose from the PC-HS01-K (black), PC-HS01-S (silver) and PC-HS01-N (gold) to complement the look of your set-up.

artikli.opis:
Napravi svoje prve korake u svijetu DJ-inga s kompaktnim DDJ-WeGO4. Saznajte kako neprimjetno miješati s taktilnim kontrolama i jogovima. Nauči korisiti sampler, Hot cues i pad FX kji je prenesen sa profesionalnog hardvera . Jednostavno priključite svoj laptop, tablet ili pametni telefon i krenite mixati

Key features

    Easy to connect

    Simply plug the DDJ-WeGO4 into your PC, Mac, tablet or smartphone with a USB cable, or connect to your iPad or iPhone with a Lightning cable and start mixing your music using the compatible DJ software or app of your choice.
    Supports WeDJ

    This controller is compatible with WeDJ, our easy-to-use DJ performance app for iPad. When connected, the app’s intuitive display makes it a breeze to mix tracks from your music.
    rekordbox dj

    You get a free rekordbox dj licence key bundled with this controller. Simply activate your licence key for our DJ software, connect the controller and start DJing.
    Simple layout, advanced control

    A host of professional features – including Hot Cues, samplers, Pad FX and loops – are packed in a compact, lightweight design. Learn to DJ on the straightforward layout and step up easily to a pro-DJ setup, including CDJ multiplayers and DJM mixers.
    PC Master Out

    For flexibility you can choose to hear your mix through your computer’s internal speakers, connected desktop speakers, or play through a wireless speaker. At the same time, you can use your headphones to cue independently of the master out.

The Pioneer DDJ-200 is the latest entry-level smart DJ controller with compatibility with Windows, Mac, iOS, and Android devices. The two-channel controller features a jog wheel, tempo slider, cue and play/pause buttons, beat sync, and eight performance pads per deck. The center section is modeled after a standard DJ mixer with a three-band EQ, channel effects (CFX), a volume fader per deck, as well as a crossfader. The headphone selection allows you to cue each deck or listen to the master mix.

For the beginner DJ, there are several features to help you achieve professional sounding mixing. Transition FX reproduce various patterns of DJ mixes between tracks, while Phrase Sync uses analyzed track information to align the start and end phrase positions of two tracks. Additionally, help is available for the novice via tutorials and pop-up hints to get you up and running in no time.

The controller is packaged with Pioneer DJ's WeDJ software for iPhone and a rekordbox dj dongle for using rekordbox dj on a Mac or Windows computer. The Pioneer DDJ-200 is USB bus powered and ships with a USB cable and a split audio cable, which allows you to monitor the cue outputs of your device while sending the main out to speakers.

    1. Multi-App Compatibility with Music Streaming Services
        Connect the DDJ-200 to your smartphone, tablet, or PC/Mac, choose your favorite from a number of compatible DJ apps such as WeDJ, MWM SAS’s edjing Mix, and Algoriddim’s djay, and control tracks stored on your device. Several streaming services are supported.
        When connected to the DDJ-200, enjoy free use of all the features in rekordbox dj and WeDJ for iPhone that normally incur in-app billing.
        DDJ-200 compatible DJ apps and their corresponding devices and streaming services
            WeDJ for iPhone: Compatible with Beatport LINK, SoundCloud Go+
            rekordbox for Windows/Mac: Compatible with Beatport LINK, SoundCloud Go+
            Algoriddim djay for iPhone, iPad, and Android: Compatible with Spotify
            edjing Mix iPhone, iPad, and Android: Compatible with SoundCloud, QQ sound, and Deezer
            WeDJ for Android: No streaming compatibility
    2. Tutorial and Pop-Hints
        Features to help beginners enjoy DJing
        Combine the DDJ-200 with WeDJ for iPhone to use the Tutorial feature, which summarizes the basics of DJing.
        Find out how to connect the controller to your devices, how to use various features and effects, and pick up tips on performance techniques.
        WeDJ for iPhone also offers the Pop-Hint feature that explains the functions of buttons without switching screens
    3. Transition FX
        The DDJ-200 can reproduce various patterns of DJ mixes between tracks for people with no experience behind the decks
        Activate the Transition FX feature in WeDJ, choose from 11 patterns, and simply slide the crossfader to switch from one track to the next via a professional-standard transition.
    4. Phrase Sync
        Phrase analysis algorithms analyze the composition of tracks and detect phrases.
        Tap the dedicated buttons in WeDJ for iPhone and Phrase Sync uses the information from this analysis to align the start and end positions of the phrases in two tracks so you can be sure it will sound natural when you switch between them.
    5. Compact and Highly Portable
        Highly portable thanks to its lightweight and slim body.
        Play sound from the built-in speaker of your smartphone, tablet, or PC/Mac.
        DDJ-200 controller can be powered via a power bank
    6. Split Output for DJ Performances
        Use split cables to separate the audio output of your smartphone, tablet, or PC/Mac into master and monitor outputs.
        Check audio via your headphones for cueing the next track, while the crowd hears the master sound playing through the speakers.

artikli.opis:
DDJ-SR
Performance DJ Controller

    16 Performance Pads provide HOT CUE, ROLL, SLICER and SAMPLER functions
    New PAD PLUS provide HOT CUE ROLL, TRANS, COMBO FX, and SAMPLER ROLL
    Large Jog Wheels for precise scratching and mixing capabilities
    Built-in 2-Channel Mixer with Crossfader Reverse
         Overview

Pioneer’s DDJ-SR 2-channel DJ controller is designed for use with Serato® DJ software. The smaller and more compact DDJ-SR inherits many of the same functions and controls of the larger DDJ-SX introduced in 2012, offering large aluminum jog wheels, integrated performance pads, and a new PAD PLUS feature that adds four additional audio effects to the performance pads..
Mixing with Serato

The DDJ-SR takes advantage of Serato DJ’s full capability, ensuring its layout of knobs and buttons are exceptionally easy-to-use with the software. 

    Performance Pads – Large rubber “performance pads” located below the big jog wheel provide HOT CUE, ROLL, SLICER and SAMPLER functions. Each soft-touch rubber pad illuminates in blue to enable users to tap the pad(s) quickly for each effect, with the output volume varying depending on the strength of each tap.
    PAD PLUS – By activating the new PAD PLUS button, the functions of the performance pads are transformed, converting the four function buttons into HOT CUE ROLL, TRANS, COMBO FX and SAMPLER ROLL. This enables DJs to trigger multiple FX with one button, and automatically sync samples and Hot Cues to the beat.  The DDJ-SR also features a Beat Indicator which gives a visual representation of the beat.
        HOT CUE ROLL/SAMPLER ROLL - Launch Hot Cues and Samples that are automatically synced to the BPM.
        COMBO FX – Simultaneously trigger and modulate multiple effects and filters with one pad.
        TRANS – Cut the volume of FX in and out at pre-set intervals.

    Big Jog Wheels – The DDJ-SR features two large jog wheels for precise scratching and mixing capabilities. The resistance for each jog wheel was fined tuned to provide users with the best “feel” and the shortest latency.
    2-Channel Mixer – The built-in 2-channel mixer on the DDJ-SR is ideal for scratch performances. The mixer can also be used with four decks using the “deck select” buttons located on each side of the controller. In addition, the unit features a “Cross Fader Reverse” switch to enable the left and right decks to be controlled from opposite sides.
    High-end Design – The DDJ-SR sports a steel top panel and an aluminum jog plate for a more elegant and stylish look and feel.

    Serato DJ Software – A free-of-charge download of Serato DJ software is included with the purchase of a DDJ-SR for an easy out-of-the-box experience.

Additional Features

    USB Power – The controller can be powered through the USB connection to a laptop.
    Built-in Sound Card (audio interface) – Simple connection to a laptop with a single USB cable.
    Adjustable Cross-fader Curve – Suits any mixing style.
    Channel Fader Start – Enables the use of the channel fader to control and play/cue tracks.
    Integrated Handles – The controller features grip handles on each side for added convenience.

artikli.naziv: DJ slušalice profesionalne PIONEER DJE-2000-W White
artikli.opis:
Pogledajte video na http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=x4djKFy-Jnk
DJE-2000
Professional DJ In-Ear Headphones

    Hybrid 2-way driver for producing clear and more precise audio quality throughout the entire frequency spectrum
    Multiple earphone tips
    Detachable cable with MMCX connector           OVERVIEW

With the clear understanding that DJs have specific audio characteristic requirements and traditionally listen to music differently, paying closer attention to the particular beats of music, Pioneer’s new inner-ear headphones were made for both their leisure music listening and for music preparation while on the go. Both models have unique design features including large high quality 9.4 millimeter drivers, replaceable and detachable cables, and interchangeable earphone tips that dampen external noise.

 
HYBRID 2-WAY DRVER

The DJE-2000 is designed with a “hybrid” 2-way driver system for producing clear and more precise audio quality throughout the entire frequency spectrum. With the use of rare and powerful magnets for its speakers, the larger 9.4 mm driver located in the back of the earphone produces low bass frequencies with impact, while the front driver efficiently generates critical mid and high frequencies so key instrumental sounds DJs pay close attention to, such as snare drums and cymbals, are more pronounced.



MULTIPLE EARPHONE TIPS

The flagship model includes three Comply™ foam earphone tips (S/M/L) to provide an extremely comfortable fit as well as reduce unwanted external sounds from entering and interfering with the original music. In addition, the model also includes four silicone tips (XS/S/M/L) and one triple flanged silicone tip to accommodate different sizes of ear canals.

 
DETACHABLE CABLE

Pioneer provides a detachable MMCX connector for maximum versatility. The cable is applied with a special textile coating that improves durability and reduces tangling and twisting.



ADDITIONAL FEATURES

    Designed to be worn over-the-ear for better fit, stability, and comfort.
    Includes carrying case, cleaning brush, and1/4" stereo plug adapter.

artikli.naziv: DJ Zvučnik PIONEER S-DJ80X, aktivan, kom
artikli.opis:
Zvučnik DM-40BT prodaju se po komadu.

S-DJ80X aktivni referentni zvučnici dizajnirani su za sjajne audio povratne informacije tijekom vježbanja DJ-ovih sposobnosti. 
Zvučnici se odlikuju izvrsnom kvalitetom zvuka, poboljšanim odzivnim bassom i pouzdanošću, 
tri vrste ulaza i ugrađenim izjednačavanjem  korisnim za DJ-eve koji žele postići najveću točnost u reprodukciji zvuka.


AUDIO QUALITY

For maximum audio performance, increased bass output and reduced unwanted resonance, each speaker utilizes a highly rigid medium density fibre-board (MDF) for the construction of its enclosure and bass reflex ducts. Additionally, to optimize sound quality and increase reliability, Pioneer uses woofers made with aramid fibre cones and soft dome tweeters infused in magnetic fluid.

Groove Technology: To improve airflow through the port of the enclosure, Pioneer engineered the port hole with grooves to help direct the sound waves smoothly. The technique decreases standing waves from the mouth of the port, resulting in smooth bass and mid-bass output, with more impact.

Convex Diffuser: Matching the bass output of the speakers, the soft dome tweeters are set in the center of a convex diffuser optimizing output and dispersing the sound energy in both left and right directions for wider imaging. The blue area below shows the normal spread of sound, and the orange area displays the enhanced spread of sound with the diffuser. For a cool cosmetic look, the diffuser also illuminates in white when the speakers are powered on.

Class AB bi-amp: Driving the speakers is a highly efficient Class AB amplifier in a bi-amp configuration to power the tweeters and woofers separately.

EQ Controls: The speakers also enable users to adjust high-pass level output via the built-in equalizer from the back of the speaker. The equalizer adjusts the high frequency range in one decibel increments (-2dB to +1dB), tailoring the audio output to the user's listening preference.
INPUTS AND EXTRAS

The S-DJ80X model features three types of inputs (XLR, TRS and RCA) for connection to different devices such as DJ equipment, computers, and portable devices. For convenience and power conservation, the speakers also include an Auto Standby mode that automatically turns itself off when there is no input signal sensed after 25 minutes and powers back on when signal input is detected.

Get more from :MOVE mini for the BBC microbit with the Bumper add-on. 
Turn :MOVE mini into a football/hockey game playing robot and compete against other robots


With this Bumper add-on for :MOVE mini for the BBC microbit, everyone's favourite little programmable 
robot buggy just got much better. 
If you were looking for an add-on that allows for competitive games, then this is the add-on for you.

Previously on :MOVE mini, we; drew shapes, controlled it via Bluetooth, control
led it with a  second microbit, and we also coded a variety of light shows. 
Now, it can totally used to play ball games too!

This self assembly Bumper add-on kit is made from the same materials as :MOVE mini and 
has been designed in keeping with the :MOVE mini aesthetic.

Once the add-on has been attached to :MOVE mini, the buggy can now easily be used for competitive 
Games involving a ball or a puck, football and hockey spring to mind.

Note:

DJI FPV sastoji se od drona, naočala i daljinskog upravljača, koji svi imaju DJI-jevu O3 tehnologiju koja pruža video prijenos s maksimalnim dometom prijenosa od 10 km, brzinom prijenosa do 50 Mbps i minimalnom latencijom unutar 28 ms. DJI FPV radi na 2,4 i 5,8 GHz i sposoban je automatski odabrati najbolji prijenosni kanal. Poboljšana sposobnost sprečavanja smetnji uvelike poboljšava glatkoću i stabilnost video prijenosa, pružajući integrirano i obuzimajuće iskustvo leta. Sadrži sustav vida prema naprijed i dolje te infracrveni sustav. Dron može lebdjeti i letjeti u zatvorenom kao i na otvorenom. Ima i opciju automatskog povratka kući. S gimbal i 1/2,3” senzornom kamerom, dron stabilno snima 4K 60fps ultra-HD video i 4K fotografije. Dron ima maksimalan let brzine od 140 km/h i maksimalno vrijeme leta od približno 20 minuta. Naočale DJI FPV V2 opremljene su zaslonom visokih performansi i podržavaju HD zaslon od 810p 120fps i prijenos zvuka u stvarnom vremenu. Primajući video signal iz drona, korisnici mogu uživati ??u pogledu iz perspektive drona u stvarnom vremenu. Naočale imaju maksimalno vrijeme rada oko 1 sat i 50 minuta. DJI FPV daljinski upravljač 2 opremljen je nizom funkcijskih tipki koje se mogu koristiti za upravljanje dronom i kamerom. Maksimalno vrijeme rada daljinskog upravljača je približno 9 sati. The DJI Mavic Pro folds down as small as a bottle of water, making it small enough to bring with you everywhere.
New OcuSync transmission system offers up to 4km of transmission range.
Fly at up to 64kmh or for as long as 27-minutes.
True 4K, fully stabilized ensures smooth footage
ActiveTrack, TapFly and other smart features make professional looking video effortless.
Obstacle Avoidance combined with sensor redundancy increases flight safety and reliability.
Vision positioning paired with GPS and GLONASS ensures precise positioning indoor and outdoors.
Fly by Phone over Wi-Fi for even easier flight

Mavic Air 2 podiže snagu i prenosivost na novu razinu, nudeći napredne karakteristike u faktoru kompaktnog oblika. Inteligentne funkcije snimanja i izvrsna kvaliteta slike stavljaju zračna remek-djela unutar dometa. Sigurniji, pametniji let omogućuje vam poboljšanje igre uz uživanje u kreativnom procesu.

Poboljšajte igru

4K / 60fps Video
Izvrsnost kroz jednostavnost

Usavrši kreativne zračne fotografije zahvaljujući glatkom 4K / 60fps videozapisu bez napora. Profil ravne boje D-Cinelike zadržava više slikovnih informacija za naknadnu obradu. Video kodek HEVC (H.265) bilježi više slikovnih informacija, koristi manje prostora za pohranu i zadržava dinamički raspon i detalje vaših snimaka, osiguravajući sadržaj na sljedećoj razini u bilo kojem trenutku.

HDR Video
Tajna nevjerojatnog HDR videa je visoka učinkovitost foto senzora Quad Bayer. Pojedinačni okvir razdvaja razine izloženosti u različitim područjima, precizno bilježeći svijetle i tamne detalje. Slike su slojevite za stvaranje šarene, uravnotežene i privlačne slike s većim dinamičkim rasponom.


48MP Fotografije
Sve je u detaljima 
Sa 1/2-inčnim CMOS senzorom, Mavic Air 2 snima impresivne fotografije od 48MP. Pripremite se za podizanje zračnog sadržaja na veću razinu.


		SmartPhoto
 
Optimizirano snimanje

Mavic Air 2 karakterizira SmartPhoto koji integrira prepoznavanje scene, HyperLight i HDR u jedan način rada za optimalne rezultate. Prepoznavanje scene optimizira različite parametre kamere za razne scene i podržava inteligentno prepoznavanje pet kategorija: zalazak sunca, nebo, trava, snijeg i drveće. 

HyperLight optimizira fotografije snimljene u uvjetima slabog osvjetljenja i HDR značajno povećava dinamički raspon i jasnoću vaše slike. Napredni algoritmi analiziraju svaku scenu, prilagođavajući parametre izloženosti i uslojavajući snimke kako bi se stvorile nijansirane, visokokvalitetne fotografije. [1]

HDR uključen
HDR isključen

SmartPhoto uključen
SmartPhoto isključen
Snažni uvjeti osvjetljenja
Slabi uvjeti osvjetljenja
HDR Panorama
Mavic Air 2 nudi DJI-ev najnapredniji panoramski način, s većim dinamičkim rasponom i bojama koje su živopisne i nevjerojatno precizne.



Mavic Air 2 ima Sony IMX586 senzor slike i podržava Quad Bayer tehnologiju, omogućavajući veći dinamički raspon i osjetljivost boja.
Poboljšani 3-osni gimbal stabilizira svaki snimak. To znači izuzetno pouzdane fotografije i videozapise, čak i u vjetrovitim uvjetima ili nepredvidivim okruženjima.

Snimite kinematografske snimke
Pratitelj fokusa
Usavrši nebo
Snimke profesionalne kvalitete bez napora zahvaljujući pratitelju fokusa. Ovaj paket inteligentnih načina praćenja, koji se jednostavno koristi, uključuje Active Track 3.0, Spotlight i Point of Interest 3.0, omogućavajući vam da oslobodite vašu kreativnost.

ActiveTrack 3.0
Praćenje predmeta izbjegavajući prepreke lakše je nego ikad s najnovijom verzijom DJI-ove ActiveTrack tehnologije. S boljim pronalaženjem puta i bržim i preciznijim predviđanjem izgubljenih predmeta, ova tehnologija zadržava vaš predmet u središtu kadra, čak i ako se oni kreću iza stabla.
Spotlight2.0
Letite slobodno dok fotoaparat ostaje usredotočen na predmet uz ovaj prikladan način. Jednostavno odaberite svoj predmet i letite, Mavic Air 2 pobrinut će se za ostalo.
POI 3.0
POI 3.0 poboljšava mogućnosti POI 2.0, posebno prepoznavanje ravnih površina. Dok POI 2.0 može izgubiti predmet tijekom praćenja, ova poboljšana značajka ne može. POI 3.0 sada može dinamički pratiti predmete poput ljudi, automobila i brodica.

Hiperlaps 8K  
Vrijeme i pokret
Mavic Air 2 podržava Hiperlapse u 8K, omogućujući vam da izobličete vrijeme i prostor za posebno zadivljujuće snimke. Najbolje od svega je to što možete postići ovaj snimak bez složene naknadne obrade. Odaberite između Free, Circle, Course Lock i Waypoint načina, odaberite mjesto snimanja, a ostalo će učiniti DJI Fly aplikacija. [2] 

Brzi snimak
Pojednostavljena mašta
Automatski snimajte kinematografske videoisječke pomoću brzog snimka. Sa samo nekoliko laganih dodira, Mavic Air 2 planira i leti složenim zračnim putem za profesionalni snimak. Dodajte glazbu, efekte i filtere pomoću super-intuitivnih  Story predložaka, kako biste svoje remek djelo mogli podijeliti izravno na društvenim mrežama.

Ikone: Dronie, Circle, Helix, Rocket, Boomerang, Asteroid

Sigurniji let za zadivljujući sadržaj
OcuSync 2.0
Nebo je granica.
OcuSync 2.0 ima udaljenost prijenosa videozapisa do 10 km, a može isporučiti i prijenos uživo rezolucije 1080p FHD, izravno s kamere drona. Uživajte više slobode za istraživanje i više jasnoće za taj savršeni snimak. [3]



Pouzdan signal, lak let
 
Mavic Air 2 podržava dvofrekventnu komunikaciju 2,4 / 5,8 GHz i automatski prelazi na najbolji kanal s najnižim smetnjama u stvarnom vremenu. [4] To značajno poboljšava sposobnost sprječavanja smetnje letjelice u izazovnim okruženjima, povećavajući sigurnost letenja.

Baterija i letenje
Letite dulje
Ostanite u zraku dovoljno dugo kako biste dobili savršeno snimanje pomoću impresivno dugog vijeka trajanja baterije do 34 minuta i  i dobijte izvrsne, brze snimke pomoću maksimalne brzine leta od 68 kph u Sport načinu. [5]

Izbjegavanje prepreka
Letite sigurnije
Mavic Air 2 svoju okolinu percipira u tri smjera: naprijed, natrag i prema dolje. Pomoćno svjetlo poboljšava vidljivost, a dodatni sloj sigurnosti koji pruža izbjegavanje prepreka idealan je za pomicanje granica onoga što je moguće. 
Naprijed
Senzor vida
Preciznost do 22 metra
Nazad
Senzor vida
Preciznost do 23,6 metara
Dolje
Senzor vida
Infracrveni senzor
 Pomoćno svjetlo pomaže pri vizualnom pozicioniranju, sigurnom slijetanju i vidljivosti u zraku. Može se ručno uključiti i isključiti.


APAS 3.0
Napredni pilotski sustavi za pomoć (APAS) 3.0 [6] koristi naprednu tehnologiju mapiranja za lako praćenje i pouzdano izbjegavanje prepreka u složenim scenarijima. Učinkovitost izbjegavanja prepreka i automatsko planiranje leta dramatično se poboljšalo u odnosu na prethodne generacije, povećavajući sigurnost i pružajući više mogućnosti.

DJI Fly aplikacija
Uređivanje bez napora
Aplikacija DJI Fly čini stvaranje besprijekornih videozapisa praktičnijim nego ikad. Ugrađeni program za uređivanje DJI Mimo nudi ručne postavke, napredne funkcije i intuitivne obrasce koji vam omogućuju stvaranje profesionalnih kompozicija u sekundi.


Dodaci
Jačanje kreativnosti 
Daljinski upravljač
Dizajniran za pilote
Novodizajnirani daljinski upravljač ima impresivno dugo trajanje baterije od 240 minuta [7] i ergonomski dizajn za udobnije prianjanje. Nova stezaljka omogućava pričvršćivanje pametnih telefona brzo i jednostavno, dok integrirane antene značajno poboljšavaju korisničko iskustvo.

ND filteri
Optimalne mogućnosti
Mavic Air 2 nudi dva ND seta filtera koji pomažu u kontroli izloženosti i pružaju veće mogućnosti za kreativnost. ND 16/64/256 set koristan je za podešavanje brzine zatvarača i pri ekstremnim uvjetima osvjetljenja, dok ND 4/8/32 set omogućuje živopisne, svijetle slike čak i s niskim ISO vrijednostima. [8]



    1. Fotografije snimljene u načinu SmartPhoto imaju rezoluciju od 12 MP. 
    2. Hiperlaps u 8K rezoluciji trenutno je dostupan samo za Free i CourseLock načine.
    3. Bez ometanja, bez smetnji i kada je u skladu sa FCC. Specifikacija maksimalnog dometa leta zamjena je za snagu i otpornost radio veze. Uvijek letite dronom unutar vizualne linije vida, osim ako je drugačije dozvoljeno.
    4. Zbog lokalnih smjernica, neke zemlje ne podržavaju prijenos od 5,8 GHz.
    5. Vrijeme leta ostvareno pod kutom od 9 ° pri brzini od 5,1 m / s, bez vjetra.
    6. APAS 3.0 i FocusTrack nisu dostupni za vrijeme snimanja u 4K pri 60, 50 i 48 fps i 1080p pri 120 i 240 fps.
    7. Životni vijek baterije mjeren je Android telefonom u okruženju bez smetnji.
    8. ND16 / 64/256 filteri uključeni su u Fly More Combo. ND4 / 8/32 set filtera može se kupiti zasebno.

Jednostavan za korištenje
X-BEE drone Fold One je brz i lagan, odlikuje se motorima bez četkica, GPS modulom i 4K kamerom sa prijenosom videa uživo.
Baterija snage 1500mAh omogućuje autonomiju leta na jednom punjenju do 15.

Novi standard mobilnosti
Dron se odlikuje nevjerojatno kompaktnim dimenzijama - 14 x 7 x 6 cm.
Zahvaljujući dimenzijama koje ne zauzimaju puno prostora dron možete ponijeti gdje god to poželite. Ručni držač namijenjen je za "dock" drona.

Učinkovita LED rasvjeta
Rasvjeta ne samo da dronu daje upečatljiv izgled, već i značajno olakšava upravljanje dronom.

Napredni GPS modul
Follow me
Odlična funkcija za sve sportske aktivnosti.

Tap to fly
Ova funkcija omogućuje odabir točki od interesa na mapi koje će dron automatski posjetiti.

Point of Interest
Dron detektira točke od interesa pomoću GPS modula i automatski započinje kruženje oko njih na visini koju vi odredite.

Headless način rada
Nakon odabira ove opcije bez obzira na koju stranu postavite pogled uvijek čete biti u mogućnosti upravljati dronom u željenom smjeru!
Ovo je odlična pomoć za početnike!

Brojne funkcije
Povratak na početnu poziciju
Zahvaljujuću ugrađenom GPS modulu pritiskom na odgovarajuću tipku na daljinskom upravljaču dron se vraća na početnu poziciju prije leta.

Automatski start
Pritiskom na odgovarajuću tipku daljinskog upravljača dron se automatski pozicionira na visinu 150 cm i očekuje vaše komande.
Ova opcija vrlo je korisna osobito u potencijalno rizičnim situacijama.

Održavanje visine
Opcija automatskog održavanja visine vrlo je korisna osobito za početnike u upravljanju dronom.
Opcija pruža potpunu kontrolu nad dronom i značajno stabilizira sliku na kameri.

4K WiFi kamera 5G dometa
Zahvaljujuću ugrađenom Wi-Fi modulu sliku uživo sa kamere možete pratiti na pametnom telefonu ili tabletu u dometu od 300m (ovisno o vrsti pametnog telefona/tableta).
Kamera se spaja putem napredne ultra brze 5G tehnologije.

Za perfekcioniste
4K rezolucija i napredni senzor jamče visoku kvalitetu snimljenih fotografija i videa.
Kamera također može snimati video i u 2.5K rezoluciji koja omogućuje veći FPS (slika u sekundi).

FPV pregled i snimanje na pametni telefon / tablet
Kamera vam omogućuje da uživo pratiti sliku na pametnom telefonu / tabletu, te pohranjivanje u memoriju pametnog telefona / tableta!
Kamera se može rotirati u širokom kutu od 90°.

Brojne sigurnosne funkcije
U slučaju slabe baterije drona ili daljinskog upravljača uređaj se automatski vraća na početnu poziciju.
Kada dron izgubi vezu sa daljinskim upravljačem također će započeti automatski povratak na početnu poziciju.

Ostalo:
- 4K Wi-Fi kamera sa prijenosom uživo (FPV) do 300m
- GPS adapter - održavanje konstantne pozicije i visine
- Autonomija na jednom punjenju baterije do 15 minuta
- Domet do 300m
- Napredne GPS značajke - Follow me, Tap to fly, POI, GEO ograda
- Back home - automatsko spuštanje i povratak na startnu poziciju
- Headless način rada
- Žiroskop: 6 - axial
- Izdržljivi motori bez četkica + auto kalibracija
- Snažna LED svjetla
- Baterija: 1x 1500 mAh 7.6V Li-Po
- Materijal: plastika
- Male dimenzije i vrhunski materijali izrade
- Masa: 0,249Kg

Sadržaj pakiranja
- dron
- daljinski upravljač
- upute za uporabu
- jamstveni list

Hook up these 8 advanced capacitive touch pads with LED indicators to start making sublime beats and control surfaces with your Raspberry Pi.

Drum HAT is the much-requested companion to Piano HAT. It uses the same capacitive touch sensor to provide 8 finger-sized drum pad
s and an indicator LED for each pad.

We added carefully-designed (we drew circles) light channels so that every pad can light up with a tap but none of the LEDs get in your way.
 It creates a really cool under-lighting effect, too!

Use it to play music in Python, control software drum synths on your Pi, take control of hardware drum machines, or just build it into an
 elaborate drum-controlled project.

Drum HAT can even be used alongside Piano HAT with a Black HAT Hack3r or Mini Black HAT Hack3r! A two-piece band in the palm of your hand.

The MagPi said that Drum HAT was an "awesome amount of fun" and gave it four stars.

Features

    8 capacitive touch pads (link each to their own Python function!)
    8 bright white LEDs (let them light automagically, or take control with Python)
    Works alonside Piano HAT
    Microchip CAP1188 capacitive touch driver chip
    Drum HAT pinout
    Compatible with Raspberry Pi 3, 2, B+, A+, Zero, and Zero W
    Python library
    Comes fully assembled

Software

We've whipped up a neat little Python library to channel your inner Phil Collins (or Nick McBrain if you're that way inclined) in literally seconds.

There's a ready-to-go example with sampled drum sounds; all you have to do is hook up a set of speakers to your Pi's headphone jack.

Get technical and Drum HAT to output regular MIDI commands via a USB to MIDI adapter, and control your software drum synths or hardware drum machine over MIDI.

artikli.naziv: DS1302 real-time clock modul / sa CR2032 (2 kom), WPI301
artikli.opis:
The DS1302 trickle-charge timekeeping chip contains a real-time clock/calendar and 31 bytes of static RAM. 
It communicates with a microprocessor via a simple serial interface. 
The real-time clock/calendar provides seconds, minutes, hours, day, date, month, and year information. 
The end of the month date is automatically adjusted for months with fewer than 31 days, including corrections for leap year. 

The clock operates in either the 24-hour or 12-hour format with an AM/PM indicator.

Features

    manages all timekeeping functions: real-time clock counts seconds, minutes, hours, date of the month, month, day of the week, 
    and year with leap year
    31 x 8 battery-backed general-purpose RAM
    simple serial port interfaces to most microcontrollers: simple 3-wire interface
    TTL compatible: VCC = 5 V
    single-byte or multiple-byte (burst mode) data transfer for read or write of clock or RAM data
    low power operation extends battery backup run time: 2.0 V to 5.5 V full operation
    uses less than 300 nA at 2.0 V
    temperature range: 0°C to +70°C

artikli.opis:
Dovoljan je mali uredjaj da bi nadogradili svoj TV sa ugrađenim DVB-T prijemnikom u uredjaj sa DVB-T2 10 bits prijemnikom. 
Mali i praktičan DVB-T2 10bits prijemnik omogućuje vam uživanje u free-to-air programima u najboljem HD kvalitetu. 
Možete ga sakriti iza TV-a, spojiti na slobodan HDMI port i kontrolirati ga putem priloženog IR produžetka. 
Jednostavno pokrenite uređaj priključivanjem na USB port TV prijemnika.

preko vanjskog uređaja za pohranu putem USB Y-kabla. 
Uživajte daljnje značajke kao što su spremanje do 400 kanala, 
rezervacije snimanja pomoću 7-dnevnog EPG-a, 4 liste omiljenih kanala, i još mnogo toga.

artikli.opis:
Električna posuda za kuhanje Nedis FCSP110EBK40, 40cm


Opis proizvoda

Električna posuda Nedis® jedan je od najsvestranijih uređaja za upotpunit vaše kuhinjsko posuđe!
Veliki kapacitet i podesiv termostat osiguravaju savršeno pripremanje manjih i velikih jela. Pogodno za perilicu posuđa i s neljepljivim premazom, pa je čišćenje brzo i bez napora.


Prženje, pečenje, pirjanje, kuhanje: ovaj višenamjenska električna posuda Nedis® pruža vam svu fleksibilnost za kuhanje onoga što želite i gdje želite - potrebna vam je samo utičnica.

Podesiva temperatura - Precizno kuhanje svih vrsta sastojaka
Za razliku od tradicionalnih štednjaka i kuhala, električna posuda može se podesiti na stalnu temperaturu koja se također može brzo prilagoditi.
Potpuna kontrola temperature kuhanja pomaže u osiguravanju savršeno pripremljene hrane bez rizika da vam večera izgori.

artikli.naziv: elektrolit 100 MF 16 V      5 x 11 mm  RM2,5
Encoder optički za Micro Metal motore, jedan par
artikli.opis:
Add quadrature encoders to your micro metal gearmotors (extended back shaft version required) with this kit.

    The installed system does not exceed the 12 mm × 10 mm cross section of the motors and extends only 5 mm beyond the plastic motor end cap.
    The 3-tooth wheel provides 12 counts per revolution;
    Using the 5-tooth wheel yields 20 counts per revolution.
    To compute the encoder counts per revolution of the gearbox output, multiply by the gear ratio
    This version is intended for use at 3.3 V.
    Because the encoder board outputs are direct phototransistor outputs, some signal conditioning is often necessary 
     between the sensor and a digital system processing the signals.

The encoder board is designed to be soldered directly to the back of the motor, with the back shaft of the motor protruding
through the hole in the middle of the circuit board. 
The better aligned the board, the better the output signal quality will be. One way to achieve good alignment is to tack down 
the board to one motor pin and to solder the other pin only when the board is well aligned. 
Be careful to avoid prolonged heating of the motor pins, which could deform the plastic end cap of the motor or the motor brushes. 
Once the board is soldered down to the two terminals, the motor leads are connected to the M1 and M2 
pads along the edge of the board, along with the power for the sensors and the two quadrature outputs

The edge connections are on a 2 mm pitch. 
The board can be soldered perpendicularly to another PCB, to a 2 mm connector, or to individual wires

Once the board is soldered to the motor, the plastic encoder wheel can be pushed onto the motor shaft. 
The encoder wheel should be pushed on far enough that the gap between the wheel and sensors is approximately 0.5 mm. 
One way to get consistent gaps is to use a few sheets of paper or a business card as a shim when installing the encoder wheel.

The best way to confirm optimal placement of the encoder wheel is to look at the signal with an oscilloscope. 
The oscilloscope capture shows what the signal outputs look like with the wheel mounted at an optimal distance from the sensors. 
Note that even in this optimal case, the signals from the two channels are different due to inherent variations in the two reflectance sensors, 
but both signals are 90° out of phase and both span a large voltage range.

Kit contains:

    two sensor boards
    two 3-tooth encoder wheels
    two 5-tooth encoder wheels

The current position of the rotary switch is going to be encoded and iussued over the outputs. The module can be soldered solidly or be used with a breadboard.

To get more information for this module, please use the link ("further information") under Downloads.

The current position of the rotary switch is coded via the outputs
Operating voltage     5 V

artikli.naziv: Epoxidna dvokomp. smjesa za zalijevanje, 100g, AG Termopasty 049
artikli.opis:
049 two-component epoxy filling compound

Two-component resin for covering and hermetisation of all components in electronics, telecommunications and radio-technics. 
It is characterized by excellent electric insulation and good adhesion to virtually all groups of materials. 
Epoxy resin is an excellent material with a very wide range of applications:
– for castings and covers to protect electrical components, such as coils, transformers, capacitors, resistors, cable ends connectors,
– excellent adhesion to a wide variety of substrates,
– good bond strength even in difficult weather conditions.
It retains its properties at high temperatures.

Viscosity in 25°C 	2000 ÷ 30000 [mPa•s]
Density in 20°C 	1,16 [g/cm3]
Number of epoxy 	0,480 - 0,510 [mol/100g]
Form            	liquid
Operating temperature 	>55°C

Instructions for use: 
Clean, degrease and dry the system. Add the content of the syringe (hardener) to the container with the covering and mix thoroughly. 
Use the prepared mass within 12-15 minutes.
The hardening time is approx. 24 hours (the hardening degree is 80-90%).
The seasoning time to complete hardening is approx. 7 days.

For hardening at a room temperature, such proportion of hardener is applied:
Filling compound 049 - 100 parts by weight
Hardener                   - 12 parts by weight
SURFACE PREPARATION
Clean a surfaces from mechanical impurities with an abrasive paper, and then degrease (e.g. with acetone)
— in the case of metals, apply chemical etching in appropriately selected bath.
PREPARATION
Thoroughly mix the components at a room temperature, in provided proportions. Prepare small portions
that will be used within several minutes.
Hardening of the composition of Filling compound 49 + Hardeningat a room temperature must be executed
in 7 days in order to obtain the full mechanical strength and in 14 days in order to achieve chemical
resistance. During the application, prepare small portions that will be used within several minutes.

artikli.naziv: FERIKLORID  0,2 litra, bočica ( željezni triklorid ili FeCl3 )
artikli.opis:
VAŽNO UPOZORENJE :
Pri radu sa ferikloridom ( željezni triklorid ili FeCl3 ) se treba pridržavati uobičajenih mjera zaštite pri radu sa kemikalijama:
obavezno treba koristiti gumene rukavice za zaštitu ruku i naočale za zaštitu od špricanja u oko ili masku sa vizirom koja štiti lice.
Prostoriju u kojoj se nagriza treba stalno provjetravati ili koristiti ventilaciju. 
Također treba koristiti zaštitnu pregaču jer feriklorid nakon nekog vremena oštećuje odjeću na mjestu špricanja.
U slučaju špricanja u oko ili na kožu, treba oko ili kožu obilno isprati vodom !!

Držati na sigurnom mjestu, dalje od dohvata djece i osoba koje se ne smiju samostalno služiti kemikalijama!!


				        UPUTA ZA UPORABU :	

Jetkanje ferikloridom obično traje nešto duže osim ako otopinu ne zagrijavate (do 60°C). 
Na sobnoj temperaturi jetkanje traje nešto manje od sat vremena.. 


Nakon jetkanja pločicu obavezno operite u čistoj vodi kako biste prekinuli jetkanje. 
Ostatke letraseta, tonera ili fotolaka možete skinuti acetonom.

Pri radu s otopinom treba osigurati mogućnost brzog ispiranja očiju i kože vodom (npr. tuševi, slavine, fontanice).

Otopina se može koristiti više puta, dok se ne primijeti da slabije nagriza bakar.

Količina od 500 ml može nagristi cca 10 dm2 bakra debljine 35um.

Metode za postupanje s otpadom :
predati ovlaštenim pravnim osobama za sakupljanje opasnog otpada ili predati u reciklažno dvorište. 
Ne odlagati s kućnim komunalnim otpadom !!
artikli.specifikacija:
VAŽNO UPOZORENJE :
Pri radu sa ferikloridom ( željezni triklorid ili FeCl3 ) se treba pridržavati uobičajenih mjera zaštite pri radu sa kemikalijama:
obavezno treba koristiti gumene rukavice za zaštitu ruku i naočale za zaštitu od špricanja u oko ili masku sa vizirom koja štiti lice.
Prostoriju u kojoj se nagriza treba stalno provjetravati ili koristiti ventilaciju. 
Također treba koristiti zaštitnu pregaču jer feriklorid nakon nekog vremena oštećuje odjeću na mjestu špricanja.
U slučaju špricanja u oko ili na kožu, treba oko ili kožu obilno isprati vodom !!

Držati na sigurnom mjestu, dalje od dohvata djece i osoba koje se ne smiju samostalno služiti kemikalijama!!


				        UPUTA ZA UPORABU :	
Otopina za nagrizanje bakrenih pločica se priprema tako da u jednoj litri vode otopite 250 grama granula. 
Jetkanje ferikloridom obično traje nešto duže osim ako otopinu ne zagrijavate (do 60°C). 
Na sobnoj temperaturi jetkanje traje nešto manje od sat vremena.. 
Ako se napravi jača otopina ( više feriklorida na istu količinu vode ), jetkanje će kraće trajati, 
ali postoji mogućnost nagrizanja zaštićenih vodova pogotovo ako su tanki.

Nakon jetkanja pločicu obavezno operite u čistoj vodi kako biste prekinuli jetkanje. 
Ostatke letraseta, tonera ili fotolaka možete skinuti acetonom.

Pri radu s otopinom treba osigurati mogućnost brzog ispiranja očiju i kože vodom (npr. tuševi, slavine, fontanice).

Napravljena otopina se može koristiti više puta, dok se ne primijeti da slabije nagriza bakar.

Metode za postupanje s otpadom :
predati ovlaštenim pravnim osobama za sakupljanje opasnog otpada ili predati u reciklažno dvorište. 
Ne odlagati s kućnim komunalnim otpadom !!
